buffaloDetails.name: MURRAH
buffaloDetails.description: The breed has a massive body, long head and neck, short and tightly coiled horn, well developed udder and broad hips.

buffaloDetails.name: JAFFARABADI
buffaloDetails.description:
The animals weigh up to 700 Kgs (average) and female animals may weigh 620 kgs
(average).
 The animal have a big dome shaped forehead with flat, thick, downwardly curved horns.
sometimes covers eyelids also.
